story.title: The Intruder - Episode 2
story.storyDescription: After a strange man knocks on the door, Eddie lands in a terrifying alternate reality where he learns an amazing secret about his father.
story.creator: web-uploader

author.bio: Jonathan Rosen is a transplanted New Yorker, who now lives with his family in sunny, South Florida. He's been writing ever since he was a little kid, but it's much more legible now.

story.prePaywallNotification: What brave actions must Eddie take before he can enter the cabin? Keep reading THE INTRUDER.
story.postPaywallNotification: Eddie is about to meet someone who will determine whether he lives or dies. Read Episode 4 of THE INTRUDER.

messages.text: Dad?
Dad are you there?
Don’t do this to me. Please. I’m not in the house anymore. I have no idea where I am.
I’m in some forest. I don’t know what to do.
DAD!!!
Eddie?
Dad, yes! I’m here!
Wherever here is.
Eddie, the first thing I need you to do is remain calm.
LOL! Yeah, Dad, no problem. A guy just tried to kill me, so I put on a necklace, and now I’m in a forest. This stuff happens all the time.
Eddie, I know it doesn’t make sense, but you have to listen to me. Especially now.
During this part, service might get interrupted a lot, but it should start to sync up soon.
This part? What are you talking about?
Dad! Are you there?
You didn’t see what I wrote?
No
Never mind. It’s the service. Do you see a stream?
Yes. It’s in front of me.
Okay, this part is very important. Once you cross that stream, there’s no turning back.
Everything starts and you have to keep going.
What are you talking about?? What do you mean I have to keep going? The start of what?
Listen to me, Eddie. If you stay where you are, you’ll never get back home.
You need to go forward. It’s your only chance.
I would tell you to stay there, and I’d try to get to you, but I’m not sure that I can.
Also, I can’t take the chance that you might be discovered before I get there.
Discovered by who? I still don’t understand.
I’ll get to that. But for right now, I need you to do a couple of things.
Do not cross that stream until you do what I tell you to do.
What things? Why do I have to cross the stream at all?
Is that the way for me to get out of here?
Dad, I’ll wait here for you. Just please come get me.
Eddie, I already told you that I don’t know if I can.
I’m going to try, but in the meantime I’m going to talk you through it.
Dad, I have no idea what you’re talking about, but you’re scaring me.
How did I turn invisible? Am I still invisible now?
No. You have to repower yourself in order to be invisible again.
Repower?? What are you talking about?
Listen to me! I know you’re scared, but it’s going to be okay. First thing is, stay quiet.
Don’t make any unnecessary sounds. We can’t have them find you.
Who??
I’ll explain after. Right now we need to get you out of there. Fast.
I wish you’d just tell me exactly what’s going on.
Dad?
Please stop wasting time. This isn’t a joke.
You’re at a level where if you die, there aren’t any resets.
WHAT?? WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT??
WHAT LEVELS??
NOT NOW!! JUST LISTEN!
Right near you there’s an old tree stump. Around four feet to your left. Do you see it?
Yes. What about it?
Okay, good. It’s hollowed out. Go over and reach in.
What’s in there?
Just do it. Reach in. You’ll feel a handle. Grab it.
Okay.
Well?
Give me a second. Okay, I’m here.
Go on.
It’s an axe! What do I need an axe for?
Mostly you’re going to use it to kill orcs and trolls.
But you will have to cut down one tree.
Yeah, okay. Seriously, what do I need it for?
I’m not joking. Keep the axe.
WHAT? Okay, I’m not going anywhere until you tell me what this is about!
Eddie, you don’t have time now!
Right now, by grabbing that axe, we’ve triggered the start.
That means you have exactly 7 minutes and 27 seconds until they find you.
And if they find you there, you’re dead.
DEAD??
Don’t be afraid. That’s not going to happen, because you’re listening to me.
Now get over to that stream immediately.
Eddie?
Eddie??
Okay, I’m here. What do I do?
Okay, you have only six minutes left.
No matter what I tell you now, just do it with no questions asked.
Okay, Dad.
You’ll see that you’re next to a small tree.
If you chop fast enough, and hard enough, you’ll cut it down in three minutes.
Then it should fall across the stream and you can cross over to the other side.
Do NOT try crossing without the tree.
Why? It doesn’t look that deep.
I SAID NO QUESTIONS! DO IT!
Okay, okay!
Hurry!
three minutes later
Okay, I just chopped down the tree.
Did it fall across the stream?
Yes.
Good.
Because that stream has piranhas in it.
PIRANHAS?
Yes. Now this is the most important part. CAREFULLY cross that tree. Keep your balance.
Just go slowly across, but no matter what, hold onto that axe.
Go. Now, you have less than three minutes.
Three minutes for what?
GO!!
two-and-a-half-minutes later
Okay, I’m across. Now what?
Buy yourself a couple of minutes. Grab the tree and pull it to your side.
two minutes later
Okay, it was really heavy, but I did it.
Good. Now they can’t follow you so fast.
But you’re going to need to move now.
Don’t be afraid when you see the arrow.
It’s going to miss you, but when it does, you need to turn and run into that forest behind you.
No matter what, don’t stop running until you get to a deserted cabin.
Follow the dirt path and you’ll reach it.
That place is a safety zone.
What safety zone? What arrow?
Holy crap! An arrow just missed my head.
RUN!
